  "detailed_description": "Being John is a 3rd Person life simulation game. Help John to regain his lost life.<br>You need to earn money, improve your relationships with people, take care of your health and improve your charisma in order to make John happy on Bozca Island.<br>To improve your relationships with people you can focus on their interests, talk to them and give them gifts. <br>To make money, follow advertisements, buy, sell or rent houses. Do sports, read books, take care of your clothes to improve your charisma.<br>It's up to you to make John happy.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784160/extras/1537a88e81b5c30752e9f8ac88786301.avif?t=1757750486\" width=550 height=308 /></span>",
